{"type":"text","timestamp":1784371255317,"sessionID":"ses_08b2f9e0bffesj9FY7WWisVCBE","part":{"id":"prt_f74d094b7001WMQt85PnQVFLjA","messageID":"msg_f74d06482001yGQ1MoEddFZRC5","sessionID":"ses_08b2f9e0bffesj9FY7WWisVCBE","type":"text","text":"The detached lineage is scoped to the supplied artifact directory. I’ll load the deep-research contract, bind the override directly, and run initialization, convergence-bounded iterations, and synthesis without writing elsewhere.","time":{"start":1784371254455,"end":1784371255314},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0189f67bd024ffba016a5b58366b5c8191ba713e83263fdabf","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784371266684,"sessionID":"ses_08b2f9e0bffesj9FY7WWisVCBE","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_Z7EltQdCmaz74yjbAa5HAULd","state":{"status":"error","input":{"prompt":"Execute the deep-research workflow as detached fan-out lineage for sk-design style library utilization, using the supplied spec folder, lineage artifact directory, session id, cli-opencode executor, convergence stop policy, maximum 10 iterations, and synthesis; write only inside the lineage directory."},"error":"MCP error -32000: Connection closed","time":{"start":1784371256533,"end":1784371266682}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0189f67bd024ffba016a5b5837480081919190e555fe6a8ec8"}},"id":"prt_f74d0981400177B3e32R07bQmu","sessionID":"ses_08b2f9e0bffesj9FY7WWisVCBE","messageID":"msg_f74d06482001yGQ1MoEddFZRC5"}}
