isting patterns?\",\"How should utilization strategies rank by leverage versus build cost after accounting for size, staleness, licensing, provenance, and extraction fidelity risks?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[],\"ruledOut\":[\"Static-manifest-only as the final relevance ranker\",\"Queryable database as canonical source of truth\",\"Semantic-only primary ranking\",\"Broad on-demand grep as the default retrieval path\"],\"focusTrack\":\"retrieval-architecture\",\"edgeCase\":\"contradictory-evidence\",\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\",\"Glob\",\"Bash\",\"apply_patch\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md:80-114,285-313\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/README.md:115-154\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/handlers/skill-graph/status.ts:114-203\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_s... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":3,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Run a bounded mode-specific relevance and context-cost ablation for deterministic eligibility, BM25 top-5 ranking, and optional semantic evidence on one pinned corpus snapshot\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.83,\"noveltyJustification\":\"4 of 6 findings were fully new and 2 partially extended the prior architecture; no simplicity bonus applied because no open question closed.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which retrieval substrate, or layered combination of substrates, best balances relevance, determinism, runtime cost, context size, and maintenance?\",\"What should the hub and each of the five modes consume, and when should a task reference one coherent real style versus synthesize selected attributes across several styles?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[],\"ruledOut\":[\"Treating the five-query aggregate P@5 as a general relevance score\",\"Interpre