ld the hub and each of the five modes consume, and when should a task reference one coherent real style versus synthesize selected attributes across several styles?\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"Unbounded mixing of top-ranked styles or averaging token values\",\"Letting corpus rank override routing, user pins, target evidence, mode standards, or live extraction\",\"Treating incidental temporal words as motion evidence\",\"Using multiple study pairs or corpus synthesis in md-generator measured phases\"],\"focusTrack\":\"mode-consumption\",\"edgeCase\":\"missing-dependency\",\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\",\"Bash\",\"apply_patch\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\"research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json:1-75\",\"research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl:1-5\",\"research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md:11-129\",\"research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json:8-548\",\"research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-4.md:6-48\",\"research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-003.md:1-103\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md:130-219\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:55-114\",\".openc... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":5,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Define and falsify an operational anti-slop proof gate for corpus use, including coherent-source fingerprinting, transformation deltas, trope limits, refusal paths, and audit integration\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.93,\"noveltyJustification\":\"4 of 6 findings were fully new and 2 partially operationalized prior evidence; closing the anti-slop question added the 0.10 simplicity bonus, yielding 0.93 after rounding.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which anti-slop rules and proof gates keep outputs distinctive rather than averaging the corpus into a generic middle?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\